FBIS4-5993 "dreas074_c_94017" FBIS-EAS-94-074 Daily Report 16 Apr 1994 North Korea WPK Sends Message to Panhellenic Movement WPK Sends Message to Panhellenic Movement SK1604113494 Pyongyang KCNA in English 1044 GMT 16 Apr 94 SK1604113494 Pyongyang KCNA English BFN [Text] Pyongyang, April 16 (KCNA) -- The Central Committee of the Workers' Party of Korea [WPK] sent a message of greetings to the third congress of the Panhellenic Socialist Movement on April 13. The message expressed the belief that the third congress would be conducive to strengthening and developing the Panhellenic Socialist Movement for peace and security, independent development and prosperity of the country and social progress. "We believe that the friendly and cooperative relations between the two parties will develop favourably in the idea of independence, peace and friendship," it said.
